text: Chantal Lafon (born 14 December 1965) is a French rower. She competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:French female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of France Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
